 bg-white shadow-2xl transform transition-transform duration-300 ease-out translate-x-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 h-16 border-b border-olive-100\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-lg\">🫒</span><span class=\"font-bold text-olive-800 text-sm\">知橄生活</span></div><button aria-label=\"關閉選單\" class=\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:bg-olive-50 text-olive-600 transition-colors\">✕</button></div><nav class=\"px-4 py-4 flex-1 overflow-y-auto\"><ul class=\"space-y-1\"><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/heritage/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">📜</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">知性史詩</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">橄欖油的文化傳承</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/science/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">🔬</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">科學萃取</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">多酚科學與健康研究</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/selection/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">🫒</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">品味鑑賞</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">EVOO 選購與品鑑</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/lifestyle/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">🍽</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">餐桌美學</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">地中海飲食生活</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/about/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">ℹ️</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">關於知橄</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">編輯團隊與使命</p></div></a></li></ul><div class=\"border-t border-olive-100 my-4\"></div><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/\"><span class=\"text-xl\">📚</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800\">所有文章</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">瀏覽完整知識庫</p></div></a></nav><div class=\"px-5 py-5 border-t border-olive-100\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full bg-olive-700 hover:bg-olive-800 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-3 rounded-xl transition-colors\" href=\"/#subscribe\">✉️ 訂閱知橄週報</a><p class=\"text-xs text-center text-gray-400 mt-2\">每週橄欖油科學精選 · 免費</p></div></div></div></div></div></header><div class=\"flex-1\"><main class=\"min-h-screen\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"name\":\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\",\"alternateName\":\"Olive Wisdom\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com\",\"description\":\"為 35+ 知性追求者打造的橄欖油科學與美學空間，以嚴謹科研實證探索地中海飲食與長壽之道。\",\"inLanguage\":\"zh-TW\",\"potentialAction\":{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"target\":{\"@type\":\"EntryPoint\",\"urlTemplate\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog?q={search_term_string}\"},\"query-input\":\"required name=search_term_string\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Blog\",\"name\":\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog\",\"description\":\"橄欖油科學、地中海美學、健康飲食智慧的深度知識庫\",\"inLanguage\":\"zh-TW\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活研究團隊\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/about\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"},\"blogPost\":[{\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"多酚衰減科學：為什麼去年的「金牌油」，今年可能只是普通烹飪油？\",\"description\":\"不談獲獎光環，我們談分子半衰期。解析特級初榨橄欖油中多酚隨時間衰減的物理過程，教您透過數據計算「真正的健康保鮮期」。\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/polyphenol-decay-science-2026\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-30\",\"image\":\"https://bnotescoffee.com/images/ai/evoo-decay-science.jpg\",\"inLanguage\":\"zh-TW\",\"keywords\":\"多酚衰減, 保鮮科學, 羥基酪醇, 2026鑑定\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活研究團隊\"}},{\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"橄欖油 vs 酪梨油：2026 年完整科學比較——哪種油真的更健康？\",\"description\":\"橄欖油和酪梨油都宣稱是「最健康的油」，但在多酚含量、發煙點、烹飪穩定性和實際健康功效上，兩者差異懸殊。本文用數據說話。\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/olive-oil-vs-avocado-oil-complete-comparison\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-29\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506484381205-f7945653044d?w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80\",\"inLanguage\":\"zh-TW\",\"keywords\":\"橄欖油比較, 酪梨油, 健康食用油, 科學分析, 2026\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活研究團隊\"}},{\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"橄欖油保存完全指南：五個你一直做錯的儲存習慣，正在偷走你的健康投資\",\"description\":\"你花了大錢買高多酚橄欖油，卻把它放在爐灶旁的透明瓶裡。本指南揭露五個最常見的保存錯誤，以及科學驗證的最佳儲存方案。\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/olive-oil-storage-guide-2026\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-29\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80\",\"inLanguage\":\"zh-TW\",\"keywords\":\"橄欖油保存, 保鮮方法, 多酚, 儲存科學, 使用指南\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活研究團隊\"}},{\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"橄欖油選購完全指南 2026：從超市到頂級莊園油，一次學會不踩雷的五步驟框架\",\"description\":\"橄欖油市場充斥著謊言。本指南用五步驟科學框架，教您在超市貨架、網路商城、甚至機場免稅店，用 30 秒判斷一瓶橄欖油是否值得購買。\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/olive-oil-complete-buying-guide-2026\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-29\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474979266404-7eaacbcd87c5?w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80\",\"inLanguage\":\"zh-TW\",\"keywords\":\"橄欖油選購, 選購指南, 高多酚, EVOO, 2026, 台灣\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活研究團隊\"}},{\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"2026 地中海抗老實踐手冊：如何在都市生活中達成 100% 橄欖多酚覆蓋\",\"description\":\"地中海飲食不僅僅是關於橄欖油。本手冊教您如何在 2026 年的高節奏都市生活中，透過數據化的飲食管理，實現端粒保護與細胞抗老。\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/mediterranean-diet-anti-aging-2026\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-29\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1490645935967-10de6ba17061?w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80\",\"inLanguage\":\"zh-TW\",\"keywords\":\"地中海飲食, 抗老, 橄欖油, 2026 指南, 細胞健康\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活 編輯部\"}},{\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"IOC 感官評鑑全解析：為什麼一瓶橄欖油的靈魂，藏在鼻尖的三秒鐘？\",\"description\":\"國際橄欖油委員會（IOC）的官方感官評鑑方法，要求品油師在 28°C 的藍色杯中，靜靜感受那三秒的香氣爆發。學會這套語言，您將不再被標籤欺騙。\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/evoo-sensory-evaluation-ioc-standards\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-29\",\"image\":\"https://bnotescoffee.com/images/ai/evoo-tasting-science.jpg\",\"inLanguage\":\"zh-TW\",\"keywords\":\"品味鑑賞, IOC感官評鑑, 特級初榨, 品油技術, 缺陷味\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活研究團隊\"}}]}</script><section class=\"relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"知橄生活 — 以科學與美學，精煉您的健康時光\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/hero-grove.webp\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-olive-900/70 via-olive-800/60 to-olive-900/80\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 text-center text-white px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><p class=\"text-gold-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4\">以科學與美學，精煉您的健康時光</p><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight\">知橄生活<span class=\"block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light tracking-[0.2em] text-olive-200 mt-2\">OLIVE WISDOM</span></h1><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-olive-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed\">橄欖油文化・地中海美學・健康飲食智慧<br/><span class=\"text-base text-olive-200\">為 35+ 知性追求者打造的橄欖油深度知識空間</span></p><div class=\"flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gold-400 hover:bg-gold-500 text-olive-900 font-